KUSA – We get it. This video is from September (the Internet has only just discovered it). But it's of a puppy attacking a pumpkin, and if you're having a bad day, it's exactly what you need right now. 
After all, you clicked on the headline. You know what you're getting. There's no need to comment that this isn't news. We know. It's a video of a cute puppy being baffled by a pumpkin. 
Anyway, to take a break from the stuff in the world that isn't an adorable puppy coming to terms with the confusing specimen which is a mini pumpkin (and that's a lot of things!), watch the video below. 
We hope it brightens up your day like it has ours: 
Can't see the video? Our bad. Watch it here: http://bit.ly/1X94mBr
